N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 455.52 - Physicians' offices and other rentals

State Regulations

This functional reporting center must contain all the
expenses associated with the provision of rental space to physicians and other
professional persons, and with other rental activities engaged in by the
residential health care facility, such as the rental of movable
equipment. (a) Standard unit of
measure. None. (b) Data source. Not
applicable. Notes
